pe":"subtitle","text":"16、胡子玉，男，53岁，家庭出身资本家，个人成份小业主，市北区淄川路粮店收款员。","index":170,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"22be0db54c","type":"paragraph","text":"一、错误事实：","index":171,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"3f5e7d4d8f","type":"paragraph","text":"1960－1963年，先后在黄台路、临邑路粮店用收粮票不发牌和偷拿收入粮票、牌等手段，贪污粮票2179斤，油票14.6斤，其中托市北区运输社王公高价出卖粮单45斤，计50.70元，油票14斤，计15.40元，共获利66.10元，自食280斤，退回粮票377斤，送亲友黄玉堂、王公等人1477斤，并换得香烟250盒，木柴250斤及点心、肉、鱼等物资。","index":172,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"0e9366bb4a","type":"paragraph","text":"二、表现情况：","index":173,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"b686a6d4cc","type":"paragraph","text":"工作不积极，服务态度不好，同志间闹不团结，运动初期订立攻守同盟，经教育坦白交代了问题，退赔较积极，退回粮票377斤，款780元。","index":174,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"1e2d15fc95","type":"paragraph","text":"三、工作组意见：","index":175,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"db8ab90b3f","type":"paragraph","text":"退赔粮票2134斤，款66.10元，不戴帽子，免予一切处分。","index":176,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"6ed2d677d5","type":"paragraph","text":"四、工作队意见：","index":177,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"9b8fdd09a6","type":"paragraph","text":"同意小组意见。","index":178,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"5ca75a9f9a","type":"subtitle","text":"17、崔成志，男，45岁，家庭出身中农，个人成份商人，文化程度高小，1954年8月至今在第三粮库任炊事员，月工资39元。","index":179,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"3b6243e231","type":"paragraph","text":"一、错误事实：","index":180,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"ccfcf35cf6","type":"paragraph","text":"60年3月－63年10月，利用在食堂管理饭菜票和采购工作之便，与总务会计芦克发勾结，先后从食堂盗窃菜票569元兑换出现金，其中除了给芦克发200元外，崔从中贪污369元。","index":181,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"a46a8793fd","type":"paragraph","text":"二、表现情况：","index":182,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"2880b02869","type":"paragraph","text":"日常工作中表现尚好，运动初期抱有幻想，曾先后两次与芦克发订立攻守同盟，企图混过关去。运动后期交代了问题，态度比较老实，并已退赔50元。","index":183,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"b83f10a36c","type":"paragraph","text":"三、工作组处理意见：","index":184,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"2304afb884","type":"paragraph","text":"免予行政处分，退赔260元，余者109元免退。","index":185,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"6b302bfbb3","type":"paragraph","text":"四、工作队意见：","index":186,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"936c6ca347","type":"paragraph","text":"同意小组意见。","index":187,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"bfb6e0b8a2","type":"subtitle","text":"18、苗秀发，男，39岁，家庭出身中农，个人成份小业主，文化程度高小，59年10月至今第三粮库工人，月工资48元。","index":188,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"550e4daa23","type":"paragraph","text":"一、错误事实：","index":189,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"73c05d9bd0","type":"paragraph","text":"1. 1960年夏季在诸城路8号黄仁梓家买棉花130斤，每斤5元，到农村以每斤7元高价出卖，获取暴利272元。","index":190,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"2ebe041716","type":"paragraph","text":"2. 1960年冬，在西吴家村托李风云代买火油300斤，每斤1.50元，到平度以每斤1.5－1.7元出售，共非法所得31元。","index":191,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"ce0deb7732","type":"paragraph","text":"3. 1961年在甘肃路20号买付效聚推车砂子3300粒，每粒0.095元，又以每粒0.115元出售，共非法所得66元。","index":192,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"608bd63bd0","type":"paragraph","text":"以上共计非法所得369元。","index":193,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"e16fe579ae","type":"paragraph","text":"二、表现情况：","index":194,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"eb7692f658","type":"paragraph","text":"日常工作表现一般，运动初期对问题认识不足，后期作了交代，态度比较老实，已退赔15元。","index":195,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"1ceb4d1606","type":"paragraph","text":"三、工作组处理意见","index":196,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"eb6fd4da6c","type":"paragraph","text":"免予行政处分，退赔200元，余者全部免退。","index":197,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"bf0f7148b6","type":"paragraph","text":"四、工作队意见：","index":198,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"25defd670e","type":"paragraph","text":"免予行政处分，退100元。","index":199,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"4d58b8e29e","type":"subtitle","text":"19、王福亭，男，44岁，家庭出身富农，个人成份资本家，现任小村庄粮店资方经理。6口人，收入93元。","index":200,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"e33e486fdc","type":"paragraph","text":"一、主要错误事实：","index":201,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"7a7f00da84","type":"paragraph","text":"自1960.1－63.2在抚顺路粮店以替班收款不下收票牌和外出预售盗窃粮单等手法，贪污1223斤（其中粮单770斤，粮票453斤）偷拿货款95.35元。其中：60年粮单350斤，粮票73斤。以上贪污粮单、粮票主要用于生活。","index":202,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"e766028d4d","type":"paragraph","text":"二、表现情况：","index":203,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"ea4ac3ac15","type":"paragraph","text":"参加工作以来思想落后，工作表现一般，面上运动交代283斤，货款56.80元。在四清运动中态度较好，有悔改表现，已退粮票50斤。","index":204,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"a4e69f2add","type":"paragraph","text":"三、小组意见：","index":205,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"23ca794acb","type":"paragraph","text":"免予一切处分，退赔150元。","index":206,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"1dc433834b","type":"paragraph","text":"四、工作队意见：","index":207,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"6781bb1b91","type":"paragraph","text":"不戴贪污份子帽子，免予行政处分，退赔现款95.35元，粮票800斤，余者免退。","index":208,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"a867412115","type":"subtitle","text":"20、范桂兰，曾用名范桂环，女，36岁，家庭出身贫农，个人成份农民，职务工人，现在米面加工厂，原籍山东省即墨县郭庄村人，现住青岛市南仲家洼1075号。7口人，经济收入月工资111元，每人平均15.90元。","index":209,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"8b92a2e28a","type":"paragraph","text":"错误事实：","index":210,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"213f9eb4c2","type":"paragraph","text":"该在本厂当工人期间利用工作之便，盗窃国家粮食1040斤，麻袋1条，面袋8条。具体事实是：","index":211,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"e37bfd9d57","type":"paragraph","text":"1. 1961－1963年，在制粉和制米车间时，利用衣服口袋、小茶缸和特制的带拉锁的布袋等，伙同王香玉、兰淑贞等人进行盗窃，3年共盗窃各种粮食1040斤，其中玉米面769斤，玉米60斤，江米20斤，江米面40斤，高粮面100斤，黄米10斤，麦子12斤，豆片25斤，小米4斤，全吃了。","index":212,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"f9edfea051","type":"paragraph","text":"2. 1961年至1963年在制粉车间伙同王香玉先后盗窃面袋16条，该分赃8条。","index":213,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"5ecc2485ba","type":"paragraph","text":"表现：","index":214,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"33fb14680b","type":"paragraph","text":"运动中态度较好，主动坦白交代，并能大胆揭发别人，已退赔人民币60元。","index":215,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"04bfb55eec","type":"paragraph","text":"组织处理意见：","index":216,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"7c2f01f1f9","type":"paragraph","text":"工作组意见：免予一切处分，经济退赔100元。","index":217,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"},{"id":"cfe791b3ee","type":"paragraph","text":"队部意见：不戴贪污盗窃份子帽子，免予行政处分，经济退赔100元。","index":218,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b"}],"page":{"id":"bc16f1501a","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d4d245361b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}